---
---

<section class="why">
  <div class="why__inner">
    <h2 class="section-title why__title">Premium quality, honest pricing.</h2>
    <p class="why__lead">
      We believe every family deserves beautiful photographs — not just those with luxury budgets. Our
      studio is built for Chennai families who value quality, warmth, and professionalism without
      compromise.
    </p>
    <ul class="why__features">
      <li class="why__feature">
        <h3>Safe, Comfortable Studio</h3>
        <p>Fully equipped for new borns, maternity & kids</p>
      </li>
      <li class="why__feature">
        <h3>On-Time, Every Time</h3>
        <p>We respect your schedule and your moments</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why {
    padding: 294px var(--figma-gutter) 120px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .why__inner {
    max-width: 910px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why__title {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .why__lead {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 18px;
    max-width: 894px;
    margin: 0 auto 62px;
  }

  .why__features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 40px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 820px) {
    .why__features {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 380px));
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }

  .why__feature {
    min-height: 138px;
    padding: 30px 40px;
    text-align: left;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background-image: linear-gradient(var(--color-bg), var(--color-bg)), var(--gradient-border);
    background-origin: border-box;
    background-clip: padding-box, border-box;
  }

  .why__feature h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 24px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .why__feature p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why {
      padding: 4rem var(--figma-gutter) 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
